reviewText: good it has jerry lewis in it
Best of Dean Martin and Jerry Lewis as an ok DVD, not the best, I guess for the age of it,, it was ok

i found this DVD splendid. I'm 35 years old and i'm italian: in Italy the tv programs never showed THE COLGATE COMEDY HOUR and watching "the best of Martin and Lewis"i had the opportunity to see how geniuses they were in lived programs.
I apologize for my bad english.
Martin and Lewis were to me the greatest comedy team when I was growing up.

THE COVER LOOKS NICE BUT THIS TOO OLD FOR ME AND IM 45 YEARS OLD. I JUST DID NOT GET A KICK OUT OF IT.OLD SONGS, BLACK AND WHITE. I INJOY THE NEWER
JERRY LEWIS ( COLOR ) NO SINGING  JUST PLAIN CLEAN FUN .  GOD BLESS, JD
